          &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;iname&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="err"&gt;忽略大小写&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="err"&gt;多个条件&lt;/span&gt;
